high_descs: Go left and then left again to stand in front of the chair with the credit card on it.
Pick the credit card up from the chair.
Go to the left and then the right and left again to stand in front of the lamp near the wall.
Turn the lamp near the wall off.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a credit card and turn a lamp off.

high_descs: Walk forward one step, turn left, walk forward to couch, turn left, walk forward to chair
Pick up credit card off of chair
Turn around, walk to middle of couch, turn right, walk to wall, turn right, walk past couch, turn right, walk to wall
Turn right facing to lamp, Turn off lamp
anns.task_desc: Walk around living room with credit card, turn off light

high_descs: Step forward, then turn left and go to the couch, then turn left and go forward to the chair.
Pick up the credit card on the chair.
Turn around and go forward, then turn right and go toward the fireplace, then turn right and go toward the dining table, then turn right and go to the wall, then turn right to face the lamp.
Look up at the lamp and turn it off.
anns.task_desc: Look at a credit card in lamp light and turn the lamp off.
